data.name: 0000 (273.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Ah… I just remembered…

data.name: 0001 (273.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: What's going on, Mikuru? You stopped all of a sudden.

data.name: 0002 (273.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Earlier, I brought everyone in the computer club tea, but…

data.name: 0003 (273.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: You did? To the computer club?

data.name: 0004 (273.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Yes. U-um, with Nagato.

data.name: 0005 (273.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Everyone was very pleased.

data.name: 0006 (273.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Yuki came with you!? Why!?

data.name: 0007 (273.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Eh? Wh-why… ask why?

data.name: 0008 (273.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Because you're our attractive mascot girl.

data.name: 0009 (273.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: So you can't do anything reckless.

data.name: 0010 (273.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: But going together with Yuki, that's hugely overkill.

data.name: 0011 (273.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: It's wasted on them.

data.name: 0012 (273.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: I'll have to properly tell her that too.

data.name: 0013 (273.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: U-umm… All she did was push the button on the teapot though…

data.name: 0014 (273.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: I think I'm imagining it clearly. She just calmly pushed the button right?

data.name: 0015 (273.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Yes. I really mean it, that's all that happened.

data.name: 0016 (273.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: That's still enough to be overkill! We need to charge extra for that!

data.name: 0017 (273.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: They're just an ordinary computer club you know.

data.name: 0018 (273.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: I'll have to thoroughly instruct you later.

data.name: 0019 (273.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Uh, this conversation went in a weird direction…
